special_powers.name: STRONGEST ONE THERE IS
special_powers.description: Hulk can use Super Strength.

special_powers.name: PUNY HUMANS STAND NO CHANCE
special_powers.description: When a character 75 points or less would deal damage to Hulk with an attack or targets Hulk with Outwit, roll a d6.  On a roll of 4-6, Hulk ignores damage dealt by that attack or Hulk ignores that use of Outwit.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO: HULK
special_powers.description: Give Bruce Banner a power action that deals no pushing damage and replace this character with IH #001 Hulk, IH #043 Hulk, or GG #027 Hulk on its orange starting line.  Existing action tokens on this character and action tokens for this action are applied to the replacement.  This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: BOMB SCIENCE
special_powers.description: Bruce Banner can use Energy Explosion.  Bruce Banner and adjacent friendly characters deal 1 additional damage to the targets of their attacks while using Energy Explosion, if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: MINION: WHEN YOU GET THROWN OUT OF GRAD SCHOOL...
special_powers.description: When a friendly character with the A.I.M. keyword and a higher point value is within 8 squares, A.I.M. Agent can use Energy Explosion.

special_powers.name: HIGH-ENERGY VISION AND HIGH ORDNANCE
special_powers.description: When attacking a character with a printed damage value of 4 or more, Hulkbuster Soldier modifies his attack value by +1 and damage dealt by this attack may not be reduced below 1.

special_powers.name: MINION: WHICH ONE JUST PUNCHED ME?
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Leader or The Leader is within 8 squares, Humanoid can use Shape Change and Willpower.

special_powers.name: BREAKING THE FOURTH WALL
special_powers.description: When She-Hulk makes an attack, after actions resolve you may destroy one square of blocking terrain or one wall that is adjacent to a targeted character.

special_powers.name: MARRIED(!?) DUO
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named She-Hulk is adjacent to John Jameson, they both modify their attack values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO: MAN-WOLF
special_powers.description: Give John Jameson a power action that deals no pushing damage and replace this character with IH 009 Man-Wolf on its orange starting line. Existing action tokens on this character and action tokens for this action are applied to the replacement. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: STARGOD, BRIEFLY
special_powers.description: Man-Wolf can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast as if he had a range value of 6 and possesses the Power Cosmic team ability.

special_powers.name: WEAPON SWAP: PUNISHER
special_powers.description: Give Punisher a ranged combat action.  After that action resolves, replace him with any character with this trait but a different collector's number on the same click number.  Existing action tokens and action tokens for that action are applied to the replacement.

special_powers.name: WEAPON SWAP: PUNISHER
special_powers.description: Give Punisher a ranged combat action. After that action resolves, replace him with any character with this trait but a different collector's number on the same click number. Existing action tokens and action tokens for that action are applied to the replacement.

special_powers.name: PROVE FEMIZONS ARE YOUR SUPERIORS
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose an opposing character that has the highest point value among all opposing characters. Thundra modifies her attack and damage values by +1 when attacking that character.

special_powers.name: RAMPAGING ASSAULT
special_powers.description: Abomination can use Charge and Flurry.

special_powers.name: HUMANOID REGROWTH CHAMBER
special_powers.description: When a friendly character whose name included "Humanoid" is KO'd, you may roll a d6 that can't be rerolled. On a roll of 5 or 6, place a character with the same name and point value on click #2 in your starting area.

special_powers.name: I CAN'T STOP YOUR BRUTE STRENGTH, BUT MY MIND IS FAR SUPERIOR
special_powers.description: The Leader can use Outwit. Once per turn, if he uses it to counter a power or ability that isn't a defense power, he can immediately use it again to counter another power or ability that isn't a defense power.

special_powers.name: PARENTAL DUO
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Hulk or Caiera is adjacent to Skaar, they all modify their attack values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: POWER OF THE OLDSTRONG
special_powers.description: When Skaar is adjacent to a square of blocking terrain, if he possesses Invulnerability, he can use Impervious instead, and if he possesses Toughness, he can use Invulnerability instead.

special_powers.name: MEDITATIVE FEMIZON TRANCE
special_powers.description: If Lyra has no action tokens when she makes an attack, she can use Probability Control during that attack.

special_powers.name: A.I.M. MUST BE PURIFIED
special_powers.description: A.I.M. Renegade modifies his attack and damage values by +1 when attacking a character that possesses a keyword or team ability that A.I.M. Renegade also possesses.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO: A.I.MARINE HULK
special_powers.description: Give A.I.Marine a power action that deals no pushing damage and replace this character with IH #100 A.I.Marine Hulk on its orange starting line. Existing action tokens on this character and action tokens for this action are applied to the replacement. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: MANY ARMS OF THE BLACK TARANTULA
special_powers.description: Give Black Tarantula a double power action.  Give him a close combat action as a free action and he may use Blades/Claws/Fangs.  After that action resolves, he may automatically break away and move up to 2 squares and then may make a ranged combat attack.

special_powers.name: DEMONIC RESURRECTION
special_powers.description: Once per game, when White Tiger would be KO'd, you may instead heal her to click #3.  If you do, at the beginning of each of your turns while she is on the map, deal 1 unavoidable damage to another friendly character.

special_powers.name: I CAN HEAR YOUR HEARTBEAT
special_powers.description: Daredevil ignores Shape Change and Stealth.

special_powers.name: NO, BEHIND YOU
special_powers.description: Daredevil can use Super Senses.  Whenever he successfully uses Super Senses to evade an attack, deal an adjacent opposing character 1 damage.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO: DAREDEVIL
special_powers.description: Give Matt Murdock a power action that deals no pushing damage and replace this character with IH #021 Daredevil, IH #031 Daredevil, or IH #103 Daredevil on its orange starting line.  Existing action tokens on this character and action tokens for this action are applied to the replacement.  This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: SUE FOR LIBEL
special_powers.description: Matt Murdock can use Outwit.  He can use it normally, or he can use it targeting a character of 75 points or less within 6 squares if he uses it to counter Outwit, Perplex, or Stealth.  (This does not require line of fire.)

special_powers.name: WEAPON SWAP: PUNISHER
special_powers.description: Give Punisher a ranged combat action. After that action resolves, replace him with any character with this trait but a different collector's number on the same click number. Existing action tokens and action tokens for that action are applied to the replacement.

special_powers.name: EACH SCAR IS A REMINDER
special_powers.description: Jigsaw can't be healed.  Each time Jigsaw takes damage, place a number of scar tokens on this card equal to the damage taken.  Before Jigsaw makes an attack roll, you may remove any number of scar tokens and choose one: modify his attack value by +1 for each scar token removed or modify his damage value by +1 for every two scar tokens removed.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO: I'VE LED AN INTERESTING LIFE
special_powers.description: Give Rick Jones a power action that deals no pushing damage and replace this character with IH #40 A-Bomb, GG #031 Captain Marvel or CW #027 Genis-Vell on its orange starting line.  Existing action tokens on this character and action tokens for this action are applied to the replacement.  This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: ARE YOU WORTHY OF 'THE GIFT'?
special_powers.description: Hercules modifies his attack value by -1 when attacking a character with a lower point value, lower printed attack value, and lower printed damage value.  When Hercules attacks a character that does not meet all of those conditions, modify his attack value by +1 instead.

special_powers.name: COWARD, COME CLOSER
special_powers.description: Hercules can use Willpower.  Modify Hercules' defense value by +1 against ranged attacks.

special_powers.name: UNLIKELY DUO
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Hercules is adjacent to Amadeus Cho, they both modify their attack values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: TIME TO CALCULATE TRAJECTORY
special_powers.description: Amadeus Cho can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast.  When he does, modify his attack and range values by +2 and his damage value becomes 1 and is locked.

special_powers.name: 7TH SMARTEST IN THE WORLD
special_powers.description: Amadeus Cho can use Outwit.  If no friendly character has a power or ability countered, he can also use Probability Control.

special_powers.name: NO, I'M CLEARLY THE STRONGEST ONE THERE IS
special_powers.description: Red Hulk can use Super Strength.

special_powers.name: TROUBLE COMING YOUR WAY
special_powers.description: Red Hulk can use Leap/Climb. If he moves 6 squares or less due to his own action, after that action resolves he can make a close combat attack as a free action.

special_powers.name: HOTTER AND HOTTER
special_powers.description: Red Hulk can use Poison. When he does, he deals 2 damage to adjacent opposing characters and 1 damage to nonadjacent opposing characters within 2 squares and line of fire.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO: RED HULK
special_powers.description: Give General Thunderbolt Ross a power action that deals no pushing damage and replace this character with IH #028 Red Hulk on its orange starting line. Existing action tokens on this character and action tokens for this action are applied to the replacement. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: THE HULKBUSTER
special_powers.description: Friendly adjacent characters of 75 points or less modify their attack values by +1 when attacking a character that can use Super Strength.  If any friendly character attacks a character named Hulk, that friendly character modifies its damage value by +1.

special_powers.name: DEPROGRAMMING
special_powers.description: Give Doc Samson a power action and choose another friendly character within 4 squares and line of fire.  That character can't be affected by Outwit or Perplex until your next turn.

special_powers.name: PSYCHOLOGICAL TRICKERY
special_powers.description: Doc Samson can use Mind Control.  When he does so, he modifies his attack value by +1, and after actions resolve he can use Outwit and Perplex targeting a character he hit with this use of Mind Control.

special_powers.name: RUTHLESS JUSTICE FOR CRIMINALS
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with The Hand keyword modify their attack values by +1 when attacking characters of a lower point value than themselves.

special_powers.name: MATT, YOU DON'T WANT TO DO THIS
special_powers.description: Daredevil can use Exploit Weakness, Leadership, and Shape Change.

special_powers.name: SAVAGE DUO
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Ka-Zar is adjacent to Shanna, they both modify their attack values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: QUEEN OF THE SAVAGE LAND
special_powers.description: Shanna modifies her attack value by +2 when attacking a character that's occupying printed hindering terrain.  Shanna modifies her damage value by +1 while occupying printed hindering terrain.

special_powers.name: THE SCENT OF BLOOD
special_powers.description: When a character takes damage from Tiger Shark's attack, you may mark that character. At the end of your turn, if Tiger Shark is within 3 squares of a character marked this way but not adjacent, you may place him adjacent to that character.

special_powers.name: BLOOD IN THE WATER
special_powers.description: Tiger Shark can use Charge. If Tiger Shark begins or ends a move action occupying water terrain, he can be given a close combat action as a free action after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: MASTER IMPERSONATOR
special_powers.description: Man-Beast can use Shape Change. If an opposing character has been KO'd by Man-Beast this game, this Shape Change succeeds on a roll of 4-6.

special_powers.name: EMOTIONAL CORRUPTION
special_powers.description: When a character takes damage from Man-Beast's attack, after actions resolve Man-Beast can use Mind Control targeting that character as a free action.

special_powers.name: MY FIRST NON-X TEAM
special_powers.description: Modify Wolverine's attack value by +1 if other friendly characters on the map possess 3 or more different team symbols among them.

special_powers.name: LUNGE
special_powers.description: When Wolverine is given a close combat action, immediately before making the attack he may automatically break away and may move up to 2 squares.

special_powers.name: INCOMING!
special_powers.description: Joe Fixit can use Leap/Climb.  After he uses it for a move action, he can use Quake as a free action.

special_powers.name: STUNNING THROW
special_powers.description: When Joe Fixit throws an object in a ranged combat attack, after actions resolve give a hit character an action token.

special_powers.name: PENANCE STARE
special_powers.description: Ghost Rider deals penetrating damage to opposing characters that have damaged a friendly character since your last turn.

special_powers.name: SURPRISE! I'M UNDER YOU!
special_powers.description: Spider-Man can use Leap/Climb.  When Spider-Man makes a close combat attack targeting a character on a higher elevation, modify Spider-Man's attack and damage values by +1.

special_powers.name: DISTRACTING BANTER
special_powers.description: If an opposing character attacked Spider-Man and missed, modify that character's defense value by -1 until that character's next turn.

special_powers.name: IMPERIAL BODYGAURD
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose a friendly character.  When that character is adjacent to Caiera, that character's defense value becomes 18.

special_powers.name: BLADE OF MY PEOPLE, POWER OF SAKAAR
special_powers.description: Caiera can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and Super Strength. When she uses Blades/Claws/Fangs while holding an object, add 1 to the d6 roll, then remove that object from the game.

special_powers.name: CAMOUFLAGE
special_powers.description: When A-Bomb is adjacent to a wall or blocking terrain, any line of fire drawn to him for a ranged combat attack is blocked.

special_powers.name: SILENT SCREAM
special_powers.description: Black Bolt can use Pulse Wave. He can use it normally, or you can give him a double power action to use it as a free action and the damage dealt becomes his printed damage value instead of 1.

special_powers.name: SHE SPEAKS FOR ME
special_powers.description: Black Bolt can use Leadership. He can use it normally, or if he's adjacent to a friendly character named Medusa and succeeds at his Leadership roll, he may instead remove an action token from each adjacent character that shares a keyword with him and add that many actions to your action total this turn.

special_powers.name: LIMITLESS RAGE
special_powers.description: Hulk can use Toughness.  Hulk ignores all damage dealt to him unless it is dealt by an attack and the attack roll is doubles, but not a critical miss.  Friendly characters cannot use Probability Control during an attack that targets Hulk.  This power can't be countered or ignored.

special_powers.name: PEACE OF THE OUTBACK
special_powers.description: Before Hulk makes a close combat attack, you may choose to modify his attack and damage values by -1.  If you do, Hulk's target can't use defense powers.

special_powers.name: GIGANTIC REACH
special_powers.description: When this character is given an action that includes a close combat attack, all squares within a range of 3 and line of fire are considered adjacent.

special_powers.name: SWAT
special_powers.description: All damage dealt by Red King causes knock back.  When the knock back path of a character knocked back in this way is stopped by another character, deal both characters 2 knock back damage.

special_powers.name: WEAKEND UNI-VISION
special_powers.description: Cosmic Hulk's line of fire is blocked only by blocking terrain and walls. Cosmic Hulk ignores the hindering terrain defense modifier when attacking.

special_powers.name: SHIELD SMASH
special_powers.description: When Winter Hulk makes a close combat attack, if his attack total is at least 4 or greater than his target's defense value, the hit character can't make a close or ranged combat attack during it's next turn.

special_powers.name: PUNY SHIELD
special_powers.description: Winter Hulk modifies his defense value by +1 against ranged combat attacks.

special_powers.name: REVERT: CAPTAIN AMERICA
special_powers.description: Give Winter Hulk a free action and replace him with a figure on a click number as listed below. Existing actions tokens on this character are applied to the replacement, which can't be given an action this turn. If the replacement is KO'd, this character's point value is scored instead.  CA001 (Current - 1), FFCA002 (Current - 2)

special_powers.name: BEAM SMASH
special_powers.description: When Hulklops makes a close combat attack, if his attack total is at least 4 greater than his target's defense value, after action resolve he can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast targeting the hit character as a free action.

special_powers.name: EYES ON THE BACK OF MY HEAD
special_powers.description: Hulklops can use Pulse Wave. When he does, he ignores elevation when drawing lines of fire.

special_powers.name: REVERT: CYCLOPS
special_powers.description: Give Hulklops a free action and replace him with a figure on a click number as listed below. GSX008 (Current - 1), FFGSX002 (Current - 3)

special_powers.name: ICE SMASH
special_powers.description: When Icehulk makes a close combat attack, if his attack total is at least 4 greater than his target's defense value, give the hit character up to 2 action tokens after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: FREEZING HIT
special_powers.description: Icehulk can use Poison.  When Icehulk hits a character that also took damage from Icehulk's Poison this turn, after actions resolve counter that character's speed powers until your next turn.

special_powers.name: REVERT: ICEMAN
special_powers.description: Give Icehulk a free action and replace him with a figure on a click number as listed below.  Existing action tokens on this character are applied to the replacement, which can't be given an action this turn.  If the replacement is KO'd, this character's point value is scored instead.  GSX038 (Current - 1), FFGSX006 (Current - 3)

special_powers.name: SEA SMASH
special_powers.description: When Hulkmariner makes a close combat attack, if his attack total is at least 4 greater than his target's defense value, the hit character gains Earthbound/Neutralized this game as long as Hulkmariner is on the map.

special_powers.name: FLOTSAM AND JETSAM
special_powers.description: Hulkmariner can use Super Strength.  Give Hulkmariner a free action if he occupies water terrain and isn't holding an object.  Give Hulkmariner a standard light object from outside the game.

special_powers.name: REVERT: NAMOR
special_powers.description: Give Hulkmariner a free action and replace him with a figure on a click number as listed below. Existing actions tokens on this character are applied to the replacement, which can't be given an action this turn. If the replacement is KO'd, this character's point value is scored instead. GG009 (Current), GG203 (Current - 1)

special_powers.name: THUNDER SMASH
special_powers.description: When Mighty Thorr makes a close combat attack, if his attack total is at least 4 greater than his target's defense value, after actions resolve he can use Quake as a free action.

special_powers.name: CHAIN LIGHTNING
special_powers.description: Mighty Thorr can use Energy Explosion as if he possessed 2 targets.

special_powers.name: REVERT: THOR
special_powers.description: Give Mighty Thorr a free action and replace him with a figure on a click number listed below. Existing action tokens on this character are applied to the replacement, which can't be given an action this turn. If the replacement is KO'd, this character's point value is scored instead.  CW038 (Current - 2), FFCW005 (Current - 1), FFHOT005 (Current)

special_powers.name: BLOOD SMASH
special_powers.description: When Wolverage makes a close combat attack, if his attack total is at least 4 greater than his target's defense value, after actions resolve heal Wolverage of 2 damage.

special_powers.name: BIG CLAWS
special_powers.description: Wolverage can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and Flurry. When Wolverage is given a close combat action, squares within a range of 2 and line of fire may be considered adjacent.

special_powers.name: REVERT: WOLVERINE
special_powers.description: Give Wolverage a free action and replace him with a figure on a click number as listed below. Existing action tokens on this character are applied to the replacement, which can't be given an action this turn. If the replacement is KO'd, this character's point value is scored instead.  CW029 (Current), FFGSX004 (Current - 1), GSX009 (Current - 2)

special_powers.name: HULK PLATOON
special_powers.description: A.I.Marine Hulk modifies his attack value by +1 for each friendly adjacent character named A.I.Marine or A.I.Marine Hulk. A.I.Marine Hulk modifies his damage value by +1 for each set of two friendly adjacent characters named either A.I.Marine or A.I.Marine Hulk. (Each character can only be counted as part of a set once.)

special_powers.name: CHARGING UP
special_powers.description: When targeted by a close combat attack, Bruce Banner can use Toughness if he has no action tokens, Invulnerability if he has 1 action token, and Impervious if he has 2 action tokens.

special_powers.name: BANNERTECH FORCEFIELD
special_powers.description: Bruce Banner can use Barrier and Energy Shield/Deflection.

special_powers.name: BORROWED ROGUES GALLERY
special_powers.description: When attacking a character possessing the Brotherhood of Mutants, Hydra, Masters of Evil, Minions of Doom, Sinister Syndicate, or Skrulls team ability, modify Daredevil's attack value by +1.

special_powers.name: LEAVE HULK ALONE!
special_powers.description: All damage dealt by Hulk causes knockback.

special_powers.name: GUNS MAKE HULK MAD!
special_powers.description: Modify Hulk's attack and damage values by +1 for each time he was targeted by a ranged attack since your last turn.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO: HULK
special_powers.description: Give Bruce Banner a power action that deals no pushing damage and replace this character with IH #201 Hulk on its orange starting line. Existing action tokens on this character and action tokens for this action are applied to the replacement. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: BANNERTECH GAMMA INHIBITORS
special_powers.description: Bruce Banner can use Incapacitate. If he uses Incapacitate to target a character with a printed damage of 4 or more, modify his attack value by +2.

special_powers.name: YOU WOULDN'T LIKE ME WHEN I'M ANGRY
special_powers.description: When Bruce Banner takes 2 or more damage from an opponent's attack, if after actions are resolved this power is revealed, you may replace this character with #201 Hulk on its orange starting line. Existing action tokens on this character are applied to the replacement.

special_powers.name: MINION: HULKBUSTERS
special_powers.description: If Hulkbuster Squad Leader is within 8 squares of a friendly character named General Thunderbolt Ross, Hulkbuster Squad Leader can activate the S.H.I.E.L.D. team ability as a free action instead of a power action.

special_powers.name: "HERE'S JENNY!"
special_powers.description: When making a close combat attack, She-Hulk can ignore walls. When she targets a character along an edge of her square with a close combat attack, after action reslove, destroy the wall between her and her target.

special_powers.name: SPRAY WITH BULLETS
special_powers.description: When Punisher makes a ranged combat attack, increase the damage dealt by 1 to each hit target character if that character is adjacent to one or more other hit target characters.

special_powers.name: SWORDS ARE MORE FUN
special_powers.description: Skaar can use Blades/Claws/Fangs. When using Blades/Claws/Fangs, if the d6 roll is less than Skaar's printed damage value, use his printed damage value as the result of the roll instead.

special_powers.name: ALTER EGO: RED HULK
special_powers.description: Give General Thunderbolt Ross a power action that deals no pushing damage and replace this character with IH #210 Red Hulk on its orange starting line. Existing action tokens on this character and action tokens for this action are applied to the replacement. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: CALL IN THE AIR STRIKE
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Thunderbolt Ross a double power action. Choose a square anywhere on the map. Modify General Thunderbolt Ross' attack value by +3 and make a ranged combat attack that does not target, and compare the result to each character occupying the chosen square or a square adjacent to the chosen square. A hit character occupying the chosen square is dealt 3 damage. Other hit characters are dealt 2 damage that causes knock back from the chosen square. Destroy all walls and squares of blocking terrain in or adjacent to the chosen square.

special_powers.name: YOUR WILL IS WEAK
special_powers.description: The Leader can use Mind Control, and doesn't take damage from Mind Control based on the point values of hit characters.

special_powers.name: I AM ALWAYS FIVE MOVES AHEAD OF YOU
special_powers.description: The Leader can use Perplex. Opposing characters can't target friendly characters' defense values with Perplex.

special_powers.name: INTENSE HEAT
special_powers.description: Red Hulk can use Poison. After an opposing character's action resolves, if an opposing character who was not adjacent to Red Hulk became adjacent to Red Hulk during that action, deal that character 1 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: NOT ABOVE USING GUNS
special_powers.description: Red Hulk may make ranged combat attacks as if he had a range value of 4.

The Gamma Bomb can't be destroyed and begins on the green starting line. At the beginning of each player's turn, if it's not disarmed, click the dial once to the right. Once per game per character, a character occupying this square can be given a free action to roll a d6. On a result of 4 or 5, click the dial 4 clicks to the left (12 is the maximum), and on a result of 6, disarm it. When the red line is crossed, deal 3 damage to each character and destroy each object, wall, and square of blocking terrain within 8 squares and then remove this object from the map.
Character can use Outwit.
